      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--ink)] leading-tight">What Does Entrepreneurial Mean? A Complete Definition and Guide to Entrepreneurial Characteristics and Mindset</h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-mute)] mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">"Entrepreneurial" describes a mindset built on innovation, risk-taking, and the capacity to spot and act on opportunity. This guide covers the formal definition, the traits that set successful entrepreneurs apart, and how the EOS framework and AI agents amplify entrepreneurial performance.</p>
